Comment: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:30.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,< Insert >
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:05.85,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Slowly, quietly, floating by
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.85,0:01:14.54,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)}Gently fading into the distant bright sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.54,0:01:23.41,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)}More fickle than the wind,\N my goal is beyond it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.41,0:01:26.50,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Let's go together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.50,0:01:32.14,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a breath and skip along,\N the world's spring breath
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.14,0:01:37.69,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun brings all our smiles together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.69,0:01:45.24,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Between "good morning" and "good bye" it's just us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.24,0:01:48.90,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}We can do whatever we want
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:55.00,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}The sunlight shining down,\N a brand new sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:02:00.74,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The morning arch we promised to meet at
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.74,0:02:08.54,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}Waving your hand at me,\N let me make today a special day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:11.68,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,600)}Let's start by talking
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:30.22,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,To the classroom, let's go, forward march
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:37.18,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey everyone, you didn't forget anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:45.57,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,The piano plays, notes ringing through the night
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:52.49,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrirror-lala, you can't solve those seven mysteries
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:15:01.88,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Say hello to that skeleton dancing by the window
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:09.05,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, good man, you're dancing with me tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:17.56,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go! It'll be fun! Just don't look behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:25.23,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,See, it's fine! Let's keep going! There's nothing to be scared about!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:34.87,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, David, Mona Lisa! Let's explore together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:22:03.83,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Next to me in the sunset, a silhouette tall as me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.83,0:22:12.64,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of another fun day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:19.81,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,I've still got so much unending stuff to talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.81,0:22:27.15,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's time for us to go home
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:34.29,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, see you tomorrow, I'll text you later
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:41.62,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's page is about all our smiles
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.62,0:22:48.92,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, see you tomorrow, thanks as always
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.92,0:22:57.47,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy we could be together today too
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.47,0:23:04.64,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Humhumhum, the wind and my heart are humming
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.64,0:23:11.90,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}At the next corner, I'll turn around and say "Bye bye"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:05.44,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:07.81,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.81,0:00:09.83,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:12.39,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? She's not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:20.95,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:25.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:26.79,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fell in here while I was sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.44,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:30.09,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:41.47,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.47,0:00:44.48,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just had an urge to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.07,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.07,0:00:48.20,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:50.98,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nice shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:23.49,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:26.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:31.15,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:38.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, your bangs got long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:43.28,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't cut them since summer vacation started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:45.28,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I cut them for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:47.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:49.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,With those scissors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.63,0:02:52.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:03:00.28,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Cut at an angle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:08.00,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... You look a lot younger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:10.18,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd look good with a ransel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:12.58,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even look like I'm in middle school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:16.17,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this. I can't go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:18.43,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer vacation right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.06,0:03:20.84,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go for one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:22.84,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! It's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:24.14,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:32.96,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tie this here, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:36.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:37.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We match!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:41.82,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We match...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:46.83,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\an8\fs70\fad(400,0)\be4\pos(800,180)\c&HFCE9F3&\3c&H9B5778&}A Midsummer Night's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.34,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:01.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:03.82,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Tooru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:07.14,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but Run is still sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:09.38,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind waking her up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:12.03,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:16.81,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan, we have to go to school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:22.40,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan, let's go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:31.58,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer, but you're still wearing these long sleeves...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:37.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that you look cuter in short sleeves...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:38.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:41.57,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:44.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll take it off! I'll take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:50.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:55.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stay awake...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:57.96,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan! The school isn't that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:05:15.29,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&H6D41C2&\3c&HCC9E9D&}Beware of\N Kidnappers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:05.82,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. There are a lot more perverts and kidnappers out during the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:09.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that some try to lure you into their car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.21,0:05:14.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so dangerous lately. We have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:20.65,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's hot out. Want a ride to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kidnapper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:32.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help! It's a pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:35.05,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.32,0:05:36.86,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pervert?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:39.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we call the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:42.30,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:44.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a nurse at their school!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:46.32,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:51.28,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll pass out these printouts. Pass them on back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:55.74,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fill those surveys out by next term.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.74,0:05:57.46,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:05:59.83,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:03.43,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a career consultation survey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:06.84,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it carefully before next term.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:10.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fill it with jokes thinking you're only in your first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:13.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't think about it, the exams will be right around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:20.38,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't try to escape from reality during the rest of your break. Study hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:24.50,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:26.41,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you next term.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.44,0:06:37.11,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitou-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:38.53,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:41.47,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you don't look well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.47,0:06:42.86,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:44.17,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:48.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's very nice. As expected of one of my students.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:51.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I've just had a slight headache since this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:54.18,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be medicine in the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:57.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,My passion should be enough for this headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:04.64,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear, Kitou-sensei. There you go wearing a lab coat again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:06.32,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my thing. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's up to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:12.67,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've been wearing a lab coat since before you came here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:16.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But lab coats are for school nurses, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:22.17,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to do something about that weird shirt pattern before you can say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:23.09,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:25.90,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to say that I have no sense of style?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:29.07,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking, Kitou-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:31.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can have Tooru-san decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:35.44,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:36.43,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uni-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:37.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:40.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitou-sensei, maybe you stepped on Uni-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:43.41,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?! What about you, Satou-sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:45.17,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, must have been you, Kitou-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:47.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was you, Satou-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:48.26,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:49.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that small.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:54.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.67,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:57.67,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,an SOS signal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:08:02.67,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a first-year classroom! I'm coming for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:08.44,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to go down to clean the erasers like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:12.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you get so dirty from cleaning erasers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:13.65,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:15.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}not{\i0} right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:18.26,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:29.09,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:33.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,This reaction... I was too hasty again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:36.62,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:41.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.79,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:46.98,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Senpai! This girl is really stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:51.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay. It was my mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:55.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got another funny story to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:57.09,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:04.90,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had stopped Yutaka from doing that.\N Then I would have spared you this embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:07.10,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:10.11,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Don't apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:13.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you apologize, it's even more embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:14.91,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:16.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:18.68,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's needs to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:20.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:23.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really looked like an SOS signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:26.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you saw it, you'd think there was a fire too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:28.95,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there were a fire, there would be smoke pouring out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:30.54,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just overreacted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:33.50,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to learn to keep your cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:34.55,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Nagi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:39.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:44.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... it's not good to panic like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:48.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! What are you doing with a hot drink in summer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:53.41,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in a rush and messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.57,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:10:00.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing good comes out of being hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:01.44,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:03.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help it in my case!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:06.58,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a disaster if there really were a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:07.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's the same for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:10.93,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot coffee in the middle of summer? Where's the sense in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:14.83,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! They should stop putting hot stuff in vending machines in the summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:15.96,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:18.79,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not the point...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.79,0:10:20.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:25.81,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(450,66)\c&H292FBC&\bord1.4}Hot-Blooded
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:25.81,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\pos(240,283)\shad2\4a&H74&\bord1.4\c&HFDFBFE&\3c&H061115&\fad(1400,0)}Confident\N in\N her\N sense\N of\N style...\N maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:31.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:34.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left my survey sheet at school...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:37.15,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:47.58,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Yuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:50.81,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left my survey sheet at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:55.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go get it, but I'm too scared to go alone. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:59.59,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. I told her not to be hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.38,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not just leave it until next term?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:07.98,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:17.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to fill it out seriously! Please! Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:22.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H161616&\bord0\fs34\fad(80,0)\frz9.619\pos(659,199)}Message Received
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs40\c&H626262&\b100\frz11.27\frx6\fry8\fad(50,0)\pos(612,298)}Nagi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs40\c&H626262&\b100\frx6\fry8\fad(50,0)\frz10.142\pos(723,336)}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs40\c&H626262&\b100\frx6\fry8\fad(50,0)\frz10.142\pos(640,451)}To school at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:27.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\frz346.594\bord0\c&H080303&\frx2\fry348\pos(787,137)\fad(250)}Message Received
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:27.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs40\c&H626262&\b100\frx2\fry348\fad(50,0)\frz345.882\pos(777,224)}Yuuko
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:27.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs40\c&H626262&\b100\frx2\fry348\fad(50,0)\frz346.213\pos(651,317)}Please{\i1\c&H3930CE&}!!!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:27.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\an4\fs40\c&H626262&\b100\frx2\fry348\fad(50,0)\frz346.213\pos(585,374)}I'm too scared\N to go alone{\c&H4039C6&\i1}!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:33.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too scared, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:38.87,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:41.38,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi's probably already there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:44.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:48.20,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Why are you two here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:50.48,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:52.82,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The front gate isn't open?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:55.89,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came in through the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:57.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The back is a pretty long walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:01.38,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko, you'd better sprint all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:04.82,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Let's go! Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.67,0:12:07.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're so impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:10.74,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Yuuko. Don't look behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:12.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:23.07,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:27.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like a new personal record.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:30.95,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's get that survey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:34.19,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... I can't move yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:35.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:41.19,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:43.46,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it's locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:54.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the staff entrance is locked too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.49,0:12:57.25,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess this won't open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:58.46,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to unlock it with?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:01.96,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:10.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The school is really scary at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:28.75,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:33.10,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I just noticed that the window was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:35.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bit unsettling, but it's good for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:37.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:39.31,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko, don't cling to me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:43.87,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't stay calm if I don't hang on to someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:45.38,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.37,0:13:49.18,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get the anatomical model from the science room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:51.48,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:52.77,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:54.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.98,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:58.20,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:01.47,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko, you're such a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:05.40,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the school is different at night than during the day! It's creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.37,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:07.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:15.29,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we don't usually see the school at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.79,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about exploring?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:20.29,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:22.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:24.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:29.09,hardsub pos,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:46.17,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it exciting being at school at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:47.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:50.86,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:56.01,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:57.54,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:01.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:05.77,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:08.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:10.65,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We'll wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:13.40,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going into the stall with you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:15.19,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:20.29,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... lights...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:21.54,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:23.15,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:28.46,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:30.30,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:40.39,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:48.24,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:48.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:49.20,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:50.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Constipated?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:52.24,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:00.93,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw a {\i1}hitodama{\i0} outside the gymnasium across campus!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:05.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were {\i1}hitodama{\i0} the things that come out right when someone dies?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:09.32,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can save them if we put it back in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:10.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:17.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}hitodama{\i0} has legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:18.55,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:20.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I want to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:20.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Footsteps...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:21.59,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}They'll find us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:23.26,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:22.66,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,A burglar?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:54.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Uni-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:58.50,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Satou-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:18:00.18,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got all scared for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.65,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing at school this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:06.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:08.77,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:12.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you left something here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:14.15,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:16.54,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, why the candle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:19.66,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I like candles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:24.02,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always think, this fleeting flame is just like my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:26.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost like we're one and the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:32.35,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:33.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acting the metaphor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:37.01,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:39.29,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? He actually collapsed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:40.30,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had an attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:41.47,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:44.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get him to the nurse's office!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:45.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pull him face down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:47.69,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll scratch his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:52.81,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's too heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:54.30,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we even lift him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:56.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:58.24,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can bring the bed here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:00.24,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:03.65,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko and I can take this side. Run, take his legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.65,0:19:05.08,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, fill in where we need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:05.95,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:06.84,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:08.17,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:09.29,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:11.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:15.50,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's too heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:23.11,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? He's suddenly lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:28.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! What about the body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:29.58,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:37.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:39.90,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:45.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:47.17,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:49.24,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hit him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:52.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serves him right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.50,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:03.68,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Sensei! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:06.36,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:06.36,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:07.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.71,0:20:09.69,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satou-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:11.67,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:13.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:16.79,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:30.96,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:33.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:34.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.61,0:20:36.46,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:41.66,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope there aren't any dogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:43.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:45.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm so tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:49.53,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:51.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:00.44,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:02.83,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:05.36,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.14,0:21:27.30,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing they all came with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:35.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I completely forgot about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.59,0:23:27.09,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I didn't get what I needed, and I got scared to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:29.17,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can't sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:37.38,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at this age, I can't ask to sleep with my parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.27,0:23:42.60,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
